The evidence with the title 'Biden's whopper in Flint, Mich. - FactCheck.org ' says Oct 20, 2011  ... In 2008 , when Flint had 265 sworn officers on the police force, there were 35 murders and 91 rapes in this city . In 2010, when Flint had only 144 police officers, the murder rate climbed to 65 and rapes — just to pick two categories — climbed to 229 . He has cited Flint's crime stats in other appearances since  ... 
